snippet.title: Best VGM 787 - Pokemon Black / White - Route 10
snippet.description:
A collection of my favorite videogame music. Note that most of them are from games I played so I might miss some great ones from games I never played.

Nintendo DS
Pokemon Black / White (2010)
Route 10
Go Ichinose, Hitomi Sato, Shota Kageyama, Junichi Masuda & Morikazu Aoki
